## 9. MONITORING & ALERTING (Issue #212)

### Prometheus Metrics

**What to measure:**
- Request count (per endpoint)
- Request latency (p50, p95, p99)
- Error rate (per endpoint)
- Database connection pool usage
- Memory usage
- CPU usage

**Alert thresholds:**
```
request_latency_p95 > 5000ms    → WARN
request_latency_p95 > 10000ms   → ALERT
error_rate > 1%                 → ALERT
memory_usage > 90%              → WARN
database_connections > 80%      → ALERT
health_check_failures >= 3      → ALERT
```

